  <brief_title>18F-FLT PET for Suspicious Findings on Mammography and Breast Ultrasound</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of 18F-FLT Positron Emission Tomography to Evaluate the Suspicious Findings on Mammography and Breast Ultrasound: A Pilot Study</official_title>
